  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed extension parapet, as a result of its size and positioning, would result in a loss of light and outlook from neighbouring dwellings contrary to LP2 &#x27;Development and Amenity&#x27; of the Hackney local plan and D6 &#x27;Housing Quality and Standards&#x27; of the London plan as well as the guidelines Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed air conditioner units by reason of their positioning and appearance are considered to be an obtrusive and incompatible form of development which would fail to respect the character and appearance of the subject property and the terrace contrary to policies LP1 (Design quality and local character) of the Hackney Local Plan 2033 (2020), D3 (Optimising site capacity through the design led approach) of the London Plan (2021) and the guidance contained within the Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009).&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
